T02D2375:10b-1: sho da sha bindu bh'a ba na n'a ma /
T02D2375:10b-3: thig le bcu drug gi nyams len zhes bya ba /
T02D2375:10b-4: yum bdag med ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2375:10b-5: rang lus khong stong bsam byas nas //
T02D2375:10b-6: mtshan med aa pa dh'a t'i la //
T02D2375:10b-7: 'khor lo bzhi ni bsam bar bya //
T02D2375:10b-8: yi ge drug cu rtsa bzhi ni //
T02D2375:10b-9: sprul pa'i 'khor lor byin gyis brlabs //
T02D2375:10b-10: bde gshegs lnga dang lha mo rnams //
T02D2375:10b-12: khams dang phung po dag pa'i phyir //
T02D2375:10b-13: dbyangs can bcu drug longs spyod bsgom //
T02D2375:10b-14: de rnams nyis 'gyur spyi bo ru //
T02D2375:10b-15: bdag nyid bsrung ba'i man ngag go //
T02D2375:10b-16: bcu drug thig le rab tu 'bar //
T02D2375:10b-17: rtsa brgyad thig le rgyu ba yin //
T02D2375:10b-18: bzhi po zhu ste rol pa gnyis //
T02D2375:10b-19: gnyis kyi phyed ni bdag med ma //
T02D2375:10b-20: bcu drug phyed phyed grangs yin no //
T02D2375:10b-21: ka nas brtsams nas ma yi bar //
T02D2375:10b-22: reg byed nyi shu rtsa lnga yin //
T02D2375:10b-23: ya nas brtsams nas ha yi bar //
T02D2375:10b-24: mi reg ming can brgyad yin no //
T02D2375:10b-25: bsdus pa a'a phyed k'a phreng gnyis //
T02D2375:10b-26: sprul pa'i 'khor lor bsam par bya //
T02D2375:10b-27: nyi ma'i 'od kyis dros tsam can //
T02D2375:10b-28: khams gsum sreg cing zhu bar bsam //
T02D2375:10b-29: tshes kyi rim pa'i rjes 'brangs nas //
T02D2375:10b-30: ri bong can gyis rgyas bar 'gyur //
T02D2375:10b-31: mkha' 'gro longs spyod bdag thim nas //
T02D2375:10b-32: dga' ba'i bdag nyid skad cig la //
T02D2375:10b-33: dpa' rgyal snying rje chen po skye //
T02D2375:10b-34: yang dag zung 'jug grub pa yis //
T02D2375:10b-35: sgrab pa thams cad dag par 'gyur //
T02D2375:10b-37: kam ka li bdag grub pa thob //
T02D2375:10b-38: kye ho ma yengs rnal 'byor pa //
T02D2375:10b-39: rang gi sems la nyams len gyis //
